- Read Paula Moraga's SpatialEpi paper (over the Shiny application)
- Convert CSV file into a data frame containing longitude, latitude, and counts
- Look into ggplot's axis break issue. Is this currently doable or do we have to make an extension? Are there any other improvements that can be done? 

